{"tid":1796970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(防被消失)被捕後要望鏡頭，不要低頭","createTime":"2019-12-25T04:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T11:45:41.000Z","uid":78222,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e35942bce73d2227d745a6fa7d78029632cf0eff","tid":1796970,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:41:16.000Z","msg":"1.搵記者相機 (相機可以zoom in同清)<br />\n2.望附近手機鏡頭 <br />\n3.就算無鏡頭都<span style=\"color: gold;\">慢慢</span>周圍擰<br />\n可能咁岩樓上影到你個樣<br />\n<br />\n要不斷慢慢周圍擰搵鏡頭 <br />\n見到相機鏡頭就望實幾秒 <br />\n方便影大頭認到你 防止被消失<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一定唔好低頭</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFx3iTA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFx3iTA.png&h=b4c2c412&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32f8dfebd1c205e50f4281724c29f7eda5d29538","tid":1796970,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記得望鏡頭呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"feadbbd04c2bfc4377b3e24802399b92b4deeb35","tid":1796970,"uid":265314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"記得望鏡頭呀"},{"pid":"ed808a1266d8549292a1ab281d5874422e66f2a5","tid":1796970,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:48:20.000Z","msg":"【置頂+重開】25/12 香港聖誕節節目<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1796892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1796892</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"455a496482548eff6bea28e0dd57c8f49437ed1c","tid":1796970,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"記得望鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警已經開始進入鳩拉mode"},{"pid":"c49e46a2e72658c68235685c0afdc148d6569d7b","tid":1796970,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"望鏡